                    <para>the ball's initial velocity (<latex>\vec{v}_{i}=<unit_number><number>10</number><unit>m·s<sup>-1</sup></unit></unit_number></latex>) towards the wall, and</para>
                  </item>
                  <item>
                    <para>the ball's final velocity (<latex>\vec{v}_{f}=<unit_number><number>8</number><unit>m·s<sup>-1</sup></unit></unit_number></latex>) away from the wall</para>
                  </item>
                </list>
                

                <para>We are asked to calculate the change in momentum of the ball,</para>
                

                <latex display="block">\Delta \vec{p}=m\vec{v}_{f}-m\vec{v}_{i}</latex>
<pspicture>
<code>
