                <para>We have everything we need to find <latex>\Delta \vec{p}</latex>. Since the initial momentum is directed towards the wall and the final momentum is away from the wall, we can use the algebraic method of subtraction discussed in Vectors in Grade 10.</para>
              </workstep>
              <workstep>
                <title>Choose a frame of reference</title>
                <para>Let us choose towards the wall as the positive direction.</para>
